  <p>To get some first insights into which direction to take with typography I utilised some simple exercises from brand
    sprints.</p>

  <p class="gap">We worked together to fill out personality sliders for the Contractuali, this was an aspirational exercise as well
    as thinking about our current positioning. This was useful because we had a quick reference for whittling down the
    thousands of typefaces out there in a selection of around 5 candidates.</p>

